Aon (Nat Watanapat) works in a convenience store. She is a lovely and intelligent girl and she also loves reading the ?How To?? guides as well -- but in her case it?s ?How To Get Rich by Yourself,? a concept that obsesses her. What will happen when these two ?How To?? devotees, with very different motivations, meet?
